HERE'S ONE AWARD HE HASN'T WON YET 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Under Mr. Buss, the Kings were the best fourth-place team in the league. Now, 
despite Gretzky and all Mr. McNall's help, the Kings are still the best 
fourth-place team in the league. 
</P>
<P>
FRED OSTERMEIER, Los Angeles 
