<HEADLINE>
<P>
CAN THE REAL EVAN COME OUT AND PLAY? 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Who untied (Single Life Columnist) Evan Cummings? 
</P>
<P>
Her columns are always interesting, but lately she is fantastic. 
</P>
<P>
Her (Jan. 19) column about the book showing older men how to date younger women 
was great, and now, this! 
</P>
<P>
(Re: the Feb. 23 column) I was hysterical relating to seeing an old flame who 
dumped me -- how many times I have fantasized he would call; he hasn't yet, but 
someday he will. And then. . . . 
</P>
<P>
Everybody at the office, men and women both loved it. Everybody read it and we 
passed it along and put it on the bulletin board. 
</P>
<P>
If this is the "real" Evan, please let her come out and "play" more often. 
She's terrific! 
</P>
