on baggage carousel at LAX. ; Photo, Rick Spring of the Customs Service plays 
tug with his mixed-breed dog, Reese. Playing is a form of reward for the 
drug-sniffing dogs. MINDY SCHAUER / For The Times; Photo, (Orange County 
Edition) Winston of the Orange County Sheriff's Department shows what he would 
do if he suspected there were drugs in this filing cabinet. ROBERT LACHMAN / 
Los Angeles Times 
</P>
