<P>
11,000 HOTEL ROOMS PLANNED FOR MEXICO 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
MEXICO CITY 
</P>
