<P>
Th newspaper said French, Japanese and Spanish chains are among the companies 
interested in investing in Mexico. 
</P>
<P>
The expansion will enable Mexico to accommodate 10 million tourists a year by 
1995. About 3 million foreign tourists currently visit Mexico annually. 
