COMMUNITY COLLEGE ROUNDUP; 
</P>
<P>
LUGO AND WILLIAMS LEAD FULLERTON IN TRACK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Jaime Lugo and Artis Williams each won three events to lead Fullerton College 
to a 99-46 victory over Saddleback in an Orange Empire Conference men's track 
meet at Saddleback. 
</P>
<P>
Long won the 1,500 meters (4 minutes, two seconds), the 800 (1:57.40) and the 
5,000 (16:25). 
</P>
<P>
Williams won the 100 (10.69), the 200 (21.9) and the long jump (21 feet 3 
inches). 
</P>
<P>
In another Orange Empire Conference men's meet: 
</P>
<P>
Orange Coast 89, Rancho Santiago 54 -- Dave Norville won the 100 (10.95) the 
200 (22.1) and the long jump (21-6 1/4) for host OCC. 
</P>
